metadata.name: WORMHOLE
metadata.description: This monster determines which character you are and which mistakes you need to learn from and takes you on a journey in time. Entry into each wormhole will result in death and you will lose your flesh. As a spirit, you return to your mistakes and evaluate them. There is no human being who has never made a mistake. This creature from outer space is giving judgment to humanity. You don't want to fall into the hands of this beast.
